  "about": {
    "details": "<p>Incorporated in 1990, Goa-based Mac Hotels Limited is a company engaged in the business of owning, operating and managing hotels, restaurants, and resorts in Goa. </p><p>The company's business includes hotels, restaurant, café, caravan site, apartment house-keeping, and related services.</p><p>Currently, the company is operating and managing one resort under the name \"Resort Park Avenue\".</p><p>The Company has entered into Management Services Agreement (OYO Agreement) with Alcott Town Planners Private Limited.</p>"
  },
